description:
The Alex Jones Show

Modnay January 19, 2009.

Alex talks with the Anglican Bishop of Jerusalem Riah Hanna Abu El-Assal about the Israeli bombardment and 

invasion of the Gaza Strip. Alex also discusses the issues of the day as we close in on the inauguration of 

president-elect Barack Obama and takes your calls.

Hour-1: News and open lines
Hour-2: open lines and Riah Hanna Abu El-Assal
Hour-3: Riah Hanna Abu El-Assal then News and open lines
Hour-4: News and open lines
